import { Component, EventEmitter, Output, NgModule } from '@angular/core'; import { Person } from '../services/person' import { formatDate } from '@angular/common'; @Component({ selector: 'app-new-account', templateUrl: './new-account.component.html', styleUrls: ['./new-account.component.css'] }) export class NewAccountComponent { @Output() OnLoginClicked = new EventEmitter(); protected password='' pessoinha : Person = { id : 0, name : '', birth : new Date, email : '', photo : '', password : '', salt : '' } checkPassword(){ } signInClicked(){ console.log(this.pessoinha); } loginClicked() { this.OnLoginClicked.emit(); } }
